data.description: Perfect and move-in-ready ! Well upgraded New roof in 2009, Water Heater 2019, All newer kitchen appliances are just 2 yrs old, and new washer and dryer, Luxury Vinyl Planks, Quartz Counter tops,Enclosed Lanai with a beautiful Sunset Views , Gorgeous and private fenced yard.The Living Room is Spacious and open , Dining Room is 13x11, Customs Shelving around the living and Dining Room( most of them convey ) New Thermostat with Wi-Fi connection, Newer Storm Door.The Plantation is an active senior community for individuals aged 55 and over. It boasts an array of amenities, including two 18-hole golf courses, an on-site restaurant, three activity centers, three heated pools, two fitness centers, and a wide variety of clubs and daily activities. Sports enthusiasts will appreciate amenities such as softball, pickleball, tennis courts, archery, shuffleboard, bocce ball, and horseshoes. There's even a woodworking shop for those with woodworking hobbies.Overall, this property offers not only a comfortable and elegant living space but also access to a vibrant and active community with numerous recreational opportunities. It seems like a great place for those looking to enjoy an active retirement lifestyle in Central Florida
